messages.content: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI-RawSaver custom node?
The purpose of the ComfyUI-RawSaver custom node is to save images as uint16 tif files.
What new functionality does ComfyUI-RawSaver add to ComfyUI?
ComfyUI-RawSaver adds the SaveTifImage function to the 'image' category in ComfyUI.
In which category can the SaveTifImage function be found in ComfyUI?
The SaveTifImage function can be found in the 'image' category in ComfyUI.
What file format does ComfyUI-RawSaver allow images to be saved as?
ComfyUI-RawSaver allows images to be saved as uint16 tif files.
Is ComfyUI-RawSaver a standalone application or a custom node for ComfyUI?
ComfyUI-RawSaver is a custom node for ComfyUI, not a standalone application.
Who is the developer of the ComfyUI-RawSaver custom node?
The developer of the ComfyUI-RawSaver custom node is LonicaMewinsky.
Does ComfyUI-RawSaver support saving images in formats other than uint16 tif?
No, ComfyUI-RawSaver only supports saving images as uint16 tif files.
